summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Yesler-Atlantic Improvement Project (Wash. R-5); authorizing of property in block 23 of H. L. yesler's First Addition to the City of Seattle, Tract 29 of Gamma poncin's Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 1 and 2 of Burke's Second Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 1 and 10 of Kaufman's Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 17 and 26 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle, Supplemental Plat, Blocks 6 and 7 of Rainier Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 4 and 7 of New Wilfred Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 1, 2, 3, 5, 6, 7, 8, 11, 13 and 14 of Jackson Street Addition to the City of Seattle, Blocks 3, 9, 19, 21, 22, 23, 24, 25, 32, and 33 of Hill Tract Addition to the City of Seattle, and portions of the Donation Land Claims of Henry L. Yesler and his wife, Sarah B. Yesler.
